Class XmlInputOutputHandler<T>

All Implemented Interfaces:
InputHandler<T>, OutputHandler<T>, XmlHandler
public class XmlInputOutputHandler<T>
extends AbstractXmlInputOutputHandler<T>

Xml Input/Output handler allows executing queries set in XML and loaded into XmlRepositoryFactory. For examples of XML query please go to the website (midao.org) or read XmlRepositoryFactory JavaDocs
